{"tid":230093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想香港改變既只係少數人，維持現狀才合符大多數人利益","createTime":"2017-05-05T06:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T14:25:39.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"545d1ed4ff61cdc110a5bb3417764af20f3cdac3","tid":230093,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"講下香港點解不能變既原因<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，維持現狀先合符大多數人利益<br />\n<br />\n1.正苦狗官<br />\n2.公墓員<br />\n3.商家<br />\n4.地產霸權<br />\n5.炒家<br />\n6.有樓人仕<br />\n7.供樓人仕<br />\n8.新移民<br />\n9.愛國人仕<br />\n10.富二代<br />\n11.廢老<br />\n12.建制/泛民<br />\n13.有錢佬<br />\n14.綜援人仕<br />\n<br />\n一大堆都支持現狀，想變既你地根本係少數<br />\n咪on9<br />\n維持現狀才合符社會整體利益，才能繼續安定繁榮"},{"pid":"9db688596f2fafa7cf7f489992bc1293f887f9a5","tid":230093,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"你肯定呢堆人加埋一齊係多數？有無數據睇睇？"},{"pid":"93faffa64d092c26bf5fb70239f7426787722c92","tid":230093,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"但人類社會進步係由小數人推動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大多數不成氣候<br />\n只係社會絆腳石，符合統結者腐敗意識<br />\n<br />\n人民從來都唔會偉大(中共就成日講人民偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n偉大只有人物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大多人只係隨大流  無知愚味<br />\n根本無信念....好易不攻自破<br />\n<br />\n唔覺係不能變"},{"pid":"7b97d260487f0dff0b0dbb1ae76c6618c3d57e7b","tid":230093,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:09:08.000Z","msg":"香港慢慢變上海工部局<br />\n<br />\n無一個會走得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc4c53bfdc3ffcbf4a4dde6a8f9130135968d93","tid":230093,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e815e9c4aaaceabfc365b7478fa96360e7d82f8","tid":230093,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"簡單講，得窮人同有錢人兩類